# Technical Specifications

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 14
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Deployment**: TBD (Vercel recommended)

## Performance Requirements
- Lighthouse score target: 90+ for all categories
- First contentful paint under 1.2s
- Fully interactive under 3.5s
- Optimize for Core Web Vitals

## Responsive Design
- Mobile-first approach
- Breakpoints:
  - Mobile: < 640px
  - Tablet: 640px - 1024px
  - Desktop: > 1024px

## SEO Requirements
- Set metadata.metadataBase for proper Open Graph and Twitter images
- Add appropriate meta tags for each page
- Ensure proper heading structure
- Optimize image alt text
- Include structured data where appropriate

## Accessibility Standards
- WCAG 2.1 AA compliance
- Keyboard navigation support
- Screen reader friendly
- Proper color contrast ratios
- Focus indicators for interactive elements
